snippet.title: 2064: Read Only Memories • Launching January 17th! (2016)
snippet.description: 2064: Read Only Memories brings the low life and high tech of Neo-San Francisco to PlayStation 4, with new stories and an all-star voice cast that brings the city to life. Coming to PS4 and PC on January 17th, learn more at http://readonlymemori.es/!
